text: Josué Alex Mukendi (born in Kinshasa) is a politician in the Democratic Republic of the Congo and was a candidate in the 2011 presidential election. He resides in Mont Ngafula, and filed for candidacy 28 November 2011. ==Sources== *Josué Alex Mukendi Category:Living people Category:People from Kinshasa Category:Democratic Republic of the Congo politicians Category:Candidates for President of the Democratic Republic of the Congo Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
